 errors, crashes, and unintended behavior.\n[Fix] Addressed an issue where a microphone could be requested despite none being available.", "created_date": 1730713000, "id": "8370407376421113", "version": "1.8.1", "version_code": 58, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5632444056884139", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8370407376421113"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1283573515524542"}]}, "change_log": "[Improvement] The intro logo section at startup is now skippable.\n[Improvement] Lip-syncing is now visible in mirrors for preview.\n[Fix] Resolved blend shape normal issues on the three new Halloween skins.\n[Fix] Fixed various minor issues to enhance overall stability.\n[Other] Internal upgrades for crash reporting and debugging.", "created_date": 1730370315, "id": "8344005362394648", "version": "1.8.0", "version_code": 57, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5632444056884139", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8370407376421113"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1283573515524542"}]}, "change_log": "[Halloween] A new multiplayer area is now accessible from the lobby! Step into a hauntingly atmospheric setting filled with jump scares and spine-tingling ambiance as you hunt for crystals and perform a ritual to unlock exclusive free cosmetics.\n[Halloween] The multiplayer lobby has received a spooky Halloween-themed makeover.\n[New Feature] Added three new Halloween-inspired skins and four new cosmetic items.\n[Improvement] Enhanced textures for stone bricks, cliff stones, wood planks, and dirt.\n[Improvement] Upgraded the fog effect for improved quality, with a refined method for fading below levels.", "created_date": 1729855995, "id": "8305062179622300", "version": "1.7.0", "version_code": 56, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}